{"quiz_metadata":{"id":65,"topic_id":1054,"title":"42nd Amendment Additions (Socialist, Secular, Integrity)","title_hi":"42वें संशोधन द्वारा जोड़े गए शब्द (समाजवादी, धर्मनिरपेक्ष, अखंडता)","description":"Explore the profound changes brought by the 42nd Constitutional Amendment Act of 1976 to the Preamble.","description_hi":"1976 के 42वें संवैधानिक संशोधन अधिनियम द्वारा प्रस्तावना में लाए गए गहन परिवर्तनों का अन्वेषण करें।","difficulty":"Moderate","total_questions":10,"time_limit_mins":10,"is_previous_year":0,"is_published":1,"created_at":"2026-07-21 15:25:21","is_premium":0,"subtopic_id":null,"version":1},"questions":[{"id":881,"quiz_id":65,"topic_id":1054,"sort_order":1,"question":"Which of the following words were added to the Preamble of the Indian Constitution by the 42nd Constitutional Amendment Act, 1976?","question_hi":"42वें संवैधानिक संशोधन अधिनियम, 1976 द्वारा भारतीय संविधान की प्रस्तावना में निम्नलिखित में से कौन से शब्द जोड़े गए थे?","option_a":"Socialist, Secular and Integrity","option_b":"Sovereign, Socialist and Secular","option_c":"Liberty, Equality and Fraternity","option_d":"Justice, Liberty and Fraternity","option_a_hi":"समाजवादी, धर्मनिरपेक्ष और अखंडता","option_b_hi":"संप्रभु, समाजवादी और धर्मनिरपेक्ष","option_c_hi":"स्वतंत्रता, समानता और बंधुत्व","option_d_hi":"न्याय, स्वतंत्रता और बंधुत्व"},{"id":882,"quiz_id":65,"topic_id":1054,"sort_order":2,"question":"Before the 42nd Amendment Act of 1976, the Preamble described India as a:","question_hi":"1976 के 42वें संशोधन अधिनियम से पहले, प्रस्तावना ने भारत को किस रूप में वर्णित किया था:","option_a":"Sovereign Socialist Secular Democratic Republic","option_b":"Sovereign Democratic Republic","option_c":"Sovereign Secular Republic","option_d":"Socialist Democratic Republic","option_a_hi":"संप्रभु समाजवादी धर्मनिरपेक्ष लोकतांत्रिक गणराज्य","option_b_hi":"संप्रभु लोकतांत्रिक गणराज्य","option_c_hi":"संप्रभु धर्मनिरपेक्ष गणराज्य","option_d_hi":"समाजवादी लोकतांत्रिक गणराज्य"},{"id":883,"quiz_id":65,"topic_id":1054,"sort_order":3,"question":"Assertion (A): The word 'Secular' was added to the Preamble in 1976, but the Indian Constitution was already secular in nature.\\n\\nReason (R): Articles 25 to 28, guaranteeing the fundamental right to freedom of religion, have been in the Constitution since its adoption.\\n\\nCodes:","question_hi":"कथन (A): 1976 में प्रस्तावना में 'धर्मनिरपेक्ष' शब्द जोड़ा गया था, लेकिन भारतीय संविधान पहले से ही प्रकृति में धर्मनिरपेक्ष था।\\n\\nकारण (R): धर्म की स्वतंत्रता के मौलिक अधिकार की गारंटी देने वाले अनुच्छेद 25 से 28, संविधान को अपनाए जाने के समय से ही इसमें मौजूद हैं।\\n\\nकूट:","option_a":"Both (A) and (R) are true and (R) is the correct explanation of (A)","option_b":"Both (A) and (R) are true but (R) is not the correct explanation of (A)","option_c":"(A) is true, but (R) is false","option_d":"(A) is false, but (R) is true","option_a_hi":"(A) और (R) दोनों सत्य हैं और (R), (A) की सही व्याख्या है","option_b_hi":"(A) और (R) दोनों सत्य हैं लेकिन (R), (A) की सही व्याख्या नहीं है","option_c_hi":"(A) सत्य है, लेकिन (R) असत्य है","option_d_hi":"(A) असत्य है, लेकिन (R) सत्य है"},{"id":884,"quiz_id":65,"topic_id":1054,"sort_order":4,"question":"The term 'Socialist' added by the 42nd Amendment refers to which brand of socialism in the Indian context?","question_hi":"42वें संशोधन द्वारा जोड़ा गया 'समाजवादी' शब्द भारतीय संदर्भ में समाजवाद के किस ब्रांड को संदर्भित करता है?","option_a":"Communistic Socialism","option_b":"Democratic Socialism","option_c":"Utopian Socialism","option_d":"State Socialism","option_a_hi":"साम्यवादी समाजवाद","option_b_hi":"लोकतांत्रिक समाजवाद","option_c_hi":"काल्पनिक समाजवाद","option_d_hi":"राज्य समाजवाद"},{"id":885,"quiz_id":65,"topic_id":1054,"sort_order":5,"question":"Consider the following statements regarding the 42nd Constitutional Amendment Act, 1976:\\n\\n1. It is often referred to as the 'Mini-Constitution'.\\n2. It amended the Preamble for the first and only time.\\n3. It was enacted based on the recommendations of the Swaran Singh Committee.\\n\\nWhich of the statements given above is/are correct?","question_hi":"42वें संवैधानिक संशोधन अधिनियम, 1976 के संबंध में निम्नलिखित कथनों पर विचार करें:\\n\\n1. इसे अक्सर 'मिनी-संविधान' कहा जाता है।\\n2. इसने प्रस्तावना में पहली और एकमात्र बार संशोधन किया।\\n3. इसे स्वर्ण सिंह समिति की सिफारिशों के आधार पर अधिनियमित किया गया था।\\n\\nऊपर दिए गए कथनों में से कौन सा/से सही है/हैं?","option_a":"Only 1 and 2","option_b":"Only 2 and 3","option_c":"Only 1 and 3","option_d":"1, 2 and 3","option_a_hi":"केवल 1 और 2","option_b_hi":"केवल 2 और 3","option_c_hi":"केवल 1 और 3","option_d_hi":"1, 2 और 3"},{"id":886,"quiz_id":65,"topic_id":1054,"sort_order":6,"question":"Which phrase in the Preamble was replaced by the phrase 'Unity and integrity of the Nation' via the 42nd Amendment Act?","question_hi":"42वें संशोधन अधिनियम के माध्यम से प्रस्तावना में किस वाक्यांश को 'राष्ट्र की एकता और अखंडता' वाक्यांश से बदल दिया गया था?","option_a":"Fraternity of the Nation","option_b":"Unity of the Nation","option_c":"Integration of the Nation","option_d":"Dignity of the Nation","option_a_hi":"राष्ट्र की बंधुता","option_b_hi":"राष्ट्र की एकता","option_c_hi":"राष्ट्र का एकीकरण","option_d_hi":"राष्ट्र की गरिमा"},{"id":887,"quiz_id":65,"topic_id":1054,"sort_order":7,"question":"In which year did the 42nd Constitutional Amendment Act, which modified the Preamble, officially come into force for the majority of its provisions?","question_hi":"किस वर्ष 42वां संवैधानिक संशोधन अधिनियम, जिसने प्रस्तावना को संशोधित किया, आधिकारिक तौर पर अपने अधिकांश प्रावधानों के लिए लागू हुआ?","option_a":"1975","option_b":"1976","option_c":"1977","option_d":"1978","option_a_hi":"1975","option_b_hi":"1976","option_c_hi":"1977","option_d_hi":"1978"},{"id":888,"quiz_id":65,"topic_id":1054,"sort_order":8,"question":"The addition of the word 'Integrity' to the Preamble was primarily aimed at:","question_hi":"प्रस्तावना में 'अखंडता' शब्द को जोड़ने का मुख्य उद्देश्य क्या था:","option_a":"Promoting economic equality","option_b":"Safeguarding the territorial wholeness and overcoming separatist tendencies","option_c":"Ensuring moral integrity among government officials","option_d":"Integrating princely states into the Indian Union","option_a_hi":"आर्थिक समानता को बढ़ावा देना","option_b_hi":"क्षेत्रीय पूर्णता की रक्षा करना और अलगाववादी प्रवृत्तियों पर काबू पाना","option_c_hi":"सरकारी अधिकारियों के बीच नैतिक अखंडता सुनिश्चित करना","option_d_hi":"रियासतों को भारतीय संघ में एकीकृत करना"},{"id":889,"quiz_id":65,"topic_id":1054,"sort_order":9,"question":"Which of the following Prime Ministers was in office when the 42nd Amendment Act amended the Preamble?","question_hi":"जब 42वें संशोधन अधिनियम ने प्रस्तावना में संशोधन किया तब निम्नलिखित में से कौन से प्रधान मंत्री पद पर थे?","option_a":"Jawaharlal Nehru","option_b":"Lal Bahadur Shastri","option_c":"Indira Gandhi","option_d":"Morarji Desai","option_a_hi":"जवाहरलाल नेहरू","option_b_hi":"लाल बहादुर शास्त्री","option_c_hi":"इंदिरा गांधी","option_d_hi":"मोरारजी देसाई"},{"id":890,"quiz_id":65,"topic_id":1054,"sort_order":10,"question":"Match the following additions by the 42nd Amendment to their core implications:\\n\\nList-I\\n(a) Socialist\\n(b) Secular\\n(c) Integrity\\n\\nList-II\\n(i) Equal respect and protection for all religions\\n(ii) Territorial and psychological wholeness of the nation\\n(iii) Commitment to end poverty, ignorance, disease and inequality of opportunity\\n\\nCodes:","question_hi":"42वें संशोधन द्वारा निम्नलिखित परिवर्धनों को उनके मुख्य निहितार्थों से मिलाएं:\\n\\nसूची-I\\n(a) समाजवादी\\n(b) धर्मनिरपेक्ष\\n(c) अखंडता\\n\\nसूची-II\\n(i) सभी धर्मों के लिए समान सम्मान और सुरक्षा\\n(ii) राष्ट्र की क्षेत्रीय और मनोवैज्ञानिक पूर्णता\\n(iii) गरीबी, अज्ञानता, बीमारी और अवसर की असमानता को समाप्त करने की प्रतिबद्धता\\n\\nकूट:","option_a":"(a)-(i), (b)-(ii), (c)-(iii)","option_b":"(a)-(iii), (b)-(i), (c)-(ii)","option_c":"(a)-(ii), (b)-(iii), (c)-(i)","option_d":"(a)-(iii), (b)-(ii), (c)-(i)","option_a_hi":"(a)-(i), (b)-(ii), (c)-(iii)","option_b_hi":"(a)-(iii), (b)-(i), (c)-(ii)","option_c_hi":"(a)-(ii), (b)-(iii), (c)-(i)","option_d_hi":"(a)-(iii), (b)-(ii), (c)-(i)"}]}